{"word":"G1392 - δοξάζω - doxázō - dox-ad'-zo - Glorify","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">δοξάζω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong>doxázō"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong>dox-ad'-zo"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong>Glorify"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - மகிமைப்படுத்து, புகழ், மேன்மைப்படுத்து, உயர்த்து"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"1. to think, suppose, be of opinion."},{"paragraph":"2. to praise, extol, magnify, celebrate"},{"paragraph":"3. to honor, do honor to, hold in honor"},{"paragraph":"4. to make glorious, adorn with lustre, clothe with splendor"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>Part(s) of speech:</strong> Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English:</strong> From <a href=\"#/G1391 - δόξα - dóxa - dox'-ah/1391\">G1391</a>; to <i>render</i> (or <i>esteem</i>) <i>glorious</i> (in a wide application): - (make) glorify (-ious), full of (have) glory, honour, magnify."},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G1380 - δοκέω - dokéō - dok-eh'-o/1380\">G1380</a>, <a href=\"#/G1391 - δόξα - dóxa - dox'-ah/1391\">G1391</a>, <a href=\"#/G1392 - δοξάζω - doxázō - dox-ad'-zo/1392\">G1392</a>, <a href=\"#/G1740 - ἐνδοξάζω - endoxázō - en-dox-ad'-zo/1740\">G1740</a>, <a href=\"#/G1741 - ἔνδοξος - éndoxos - en'-dox-os/1741\">G1741</a>, <a href=\"#/G3861 - παράδοξος - parádoxos - par-ad'-ox-os/3861\">G3861</a>, <a href=\"#/G4888 - συνδοξάζω - syndoxázō - soon-dox-ad'-zo/4888\">G4888</a>"}]}